	format: 'table') ~> SourceStagingCategory
SourceStagingBuilding, SourceHubBuilding lookup(ID == Building_ID,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LookupBuildingSqnr
SourceHubCategory, SourceStagingCategory lookup(SourceHubCategory@Category_ID == SourceStagingCategory@Category_ID,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LookupCategoryId
LookupBuildingSqnr, LookupCategoryId lookup(ID == SourceStagingCategory@Building_ID,
	multiple: false,
	pickup: 'any',
	broadcast: 'auto')~> LookupBuildingId
LookupBuildingId sink(input(
		Building_sqnr as integer,
		Category_sqnr as integer,
		Load_date_timestamp as timestamp,
		Record_source as string
	),
	allowSchemaDrift: true,
	validateSchema: false,
	deletable:false,
	insertable:true,
	updateable:false,
	upsertable:false,
	format: 'table',
	skipDuplicateMapInputs: true,
	skipDuplicateMapOutputs: true) ~> SinkLinkBuildingDetails
